    "title": "Kusema",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "kusema",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Baadhi ya watu wanaamini kwamba maneno hayawezi kuleta madhara. Hata hivyo, maandiko yanatoa mtazamo tofauti. Maneno yana uwezo wa kuleta &quot;uzima na mauti&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:21\">Mithali 18:21</a>).</p><p>Mithali inaorodhesha mambo mengi tunayosema ambayo husababisha madhara:</p><ul><li><p>uongo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:5\">Mithali 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:25\">25</a>)</p></li><li><p>mabishano (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:17\">Mithali 26:17</a>)</p></li><li><p>matusi au laana (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:20\">Mithali 20:20</a>)</p></li><li><p>kusema uongo kuhusu mtu ili kuharibu sifa yake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:18\">Mithali 10:18</a>)</p></li><li><p>kusambaza taarifa za kibinafsi kuhusu wengine au hadithi ambazo hazijathibitishwa zinazotolewa kutoka kwa mtu mmoja hadi mwingine (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:13\">Mithali 11:13</a>;<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:8\"> 18:8</a>)</p></li><li><p>sifa nyingi au zisizo za kweli zinazotolewa ili kumdanganya mtu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:21-Prov7:22\">Mithali 7:21–22</a>)</p></li><li><p>kujisifu sana kuhusu nafsi yako (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:23\">Mithali 26:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:2\">27:2</a>)</p></li></ul><p>Kitabu cha Mithali mara nyingi kinasisitiza kwamba watu wapumbavu husema mambo ya kipumbavu. “Mwanamke aitwaye Upumbavu” anawakilisha watu hawa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:13-Prov9:18\">9:13–18</a>). Anadanganya na kupotosha ili kuwadhuru wasikilizaji wake. Maneno yanaonyesha hali ya moyo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:23\">16:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:4\">18:4</a>).</p><p>Mtu anaweza kuficha nia mbaya kwa maneno ya kupendeza (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:23\">26:23</a>). Hata hivyo, tabia ya kweli itaonekana mwishowe (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:24-Prov26:26\">26:24–26</a>). Maneno ya kijinga yanaweza kuwaumiza wengine na hatimaye kumuumiza msemaji. Ulimi umejaa uovu ambao unaweza kuharibu maisha yako (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:6\">Yakobo 3:6</a>).</p><p>Kinyume chake, watu wenye hekima huzungumza maneno yanayotoa uhai, kama inavyoonyeshwa na hekima (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:7-Prov8:9\">Mithali 8:7–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:11\">10:11</a>). Watu wenye hekima hutumia maneno yao kwa uangalifu na mara nyingi ni wapole (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:27-Prov17:28\">17:27–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:4\">15:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:24\">16:24</a>). Hata hivyo, mtu mwenye hekima pia anajua wakati unaofaa wa kuzungumza (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:23\">15:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:11\">25:11</a>). Mtu huyu anaelewa kwamba wakati mwingine hata ukosoaji mkali ni muhimu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:5\">27:5</a>). Kitabu cha Mithali kwa hekima kinawakumbusha wasomaji kutilia maanani si tu kile wanachosema bali pia jinsi na wakati wanapokisema.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:21-Prov7:22\">Methali 7:21–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:7-Prov8:9\">8:7–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:13-Prov9:18\">9:13–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:11\">10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:18\">18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:13\">11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:5\">14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:25\">25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:4\">15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:23\">23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:23-Prov16:24\">16:23–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:28\">17:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:4\">18:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:21\">21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:20\">20:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:11\">25:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:17\">26:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:23-Prov26:26\">23–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:2\">27:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:5\">5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:33-Matt12:37\">Mathayo 12:33–37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:1-Jas3:12\">Yakobo 3:1–12</a></p>",
